summary: How Ice Dragon Easily Break The Wall?
title: How Ice Dragon Easily Break The Wall?
body:
How Ice Dragon Easily Break The Wall?

In the last episode of Season 7, we saw that Night King easily break the wall in the north with the help of his Ice Dragon (Dead Viserion). But this wall was not made so easily. So how did that dragon break the big wall easily? Let’s know about it –

Wall is Made from Ice Not From Stone HBO

It is said that this wall was built by ‘Brandon The Builder’. For this, he got the help of children…

summary: Got to Get My Heart Back
title: Got to Get My Heart Back
body:
Matt and Val split up. He has a son named Owen. Centered around Val and Matt Breaking up and what happens in his life past that point. I’M BAD AT DESCRIBING SO LET THE STORY DO THE TALKING :)

CHAPTER 1

Val, I’m home!’ i shout. She doesn’t answer but i know she’s here becausei can hear her voice. She’s giggling so it made me wonder whetheror not she heard me and decided to hide. I made my way up…

Read more…
